“It is our way of giving back to the community,” André McDonald, retail officer of Eskort, said. The sponsorship forms part of Eskort’s social responsibility project. “We are very proud to be part of this community. This sponsorship is for the community, by the community,” McDonald said. Natacha Bouwer, marketing officer of Lowveld High, expressed the school’s gratitude towards Eskort for its continuous support over the years. “Our team will wear their kit with pride,” she said. “We look forward to a great season ahead.”